# Styling Guidelines

The website follows a clean, modern design with consistent styling throughout all sections.

## CSS Organization

The [styles.css](mdc:styles.css) file contains all styling for the website, organized into logical sections:

1. Global styles and variables
2. Header and navigation styles
3. Section-specific styles
4. Responsive design rules

## Key Style Components

### Layout
- Container-based layout with max-width for content
- Responsive grid and flexbox for content organization
- Section-based organization with consistent spacing

### Typography
- Primary font: Inter (Google Fonts)
- Font Awesome for icons

### Color Scheme
- Primary accent color: #0060df (blue)
- Secondary colors: #e5edfb (light blue), #333333 (dark gray)
- Text colors: #333333 (primary), #666666 (secondary)

### Interactive Elements
- Publication filtering buttons
- Navigation with active state tracking
- Smooth scrolling behavior

## Responsive Design

The website is fully responsive with:
- Optimized mobile navigation with horizontal scrolling
- Adaptive layouts for different screen sizes
- Smart active link centering on mobile
- Media queries for different device sizes
